Independent Newspapers Awards 2021 holding at Eko Hotel and Suites, Victoria Island, today, Saturday, March 5, 2022. The ceremony, themed ‘Celebrating Trailblazers,’ is billed to kick off at 6 pm with a red carpet event at the Convention Centre of the prestigious Eko Hotel and Suites, Victoria Island, Lagos. Independent Newspapers Limited (INL), publishers of Daily Independent, Saturday Independent and Sunday Independent titles, bestow honours on eminent Nigerian individual and corporate citizens who have distinguished themselves as leaders and true servants of the people in their various domains and fields of endeavours. Independent Newspapers Award Night 2021 [PHOTO NEWS] LIST OF AWARDEES AND THEIR AWARDS